result.adr_address: 534號 Nathan Rd, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 534號 Nathan Rd, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong
result.name: Old Street

reviews.text:
Imagine Taiwan is right in Hong Kong. What would it be like? Today, this restaurant - Old Street - is exactly that. We tried some of the most authentic Taiwanese food, and here’s a brief review. 

Taiwanese Beef Noodles - I absolutely love this. Whenever I go to a Taiwanese restaurant, I always order this. The beef is braised long enough to be very tender, whereas the soup complements the noodles and the beef very well. Well done. 

Braised pork belly rice - this is another favorite dish of mine. I love how the braised pork taste like. I’m not sure how to describe its taste, but it definitely tastes like home. 

Taiwanese preserved egg with tofu - it’s cold dish is amazing. If you never tried this dish, you have to. The preserved egg complements the tofu very well. 

Taiwanese fried mixed platter - this has the best of the fried street food you can have in Taiwan. Squids ball, fried chicken and fried tofu all in one plant. It’s a happy meal what can I say. 

Braised pork with lettuce - this is basically the braised pork you found in the braised pork rice, but with the vegetable. I like how the braised pork makes the veggie taste so much better. If your kids don’t like veggies, this is it. 

I’ll give this restaurant a green light. It’s affordable, high quality and the staffs are very polite.
Tasty food. Authentic Taiwanese food.
the taiwan beef noodle is very good, one of the best.
Taste OK and reasonable price in town centre.  But my friend said that his ordered noodle soup was not hot!
good food

result.adr_address: 香港油麻地彌敦道534號
result.name: 老街

reviews.text:
Went there for dinner.
Loud music and not so friendly staff.
用餐時已接近九時，所以點餐後很快上菜。
冷氣開得非常大，而且音樂開得好大聲。待應不太友善，不走近客人只願隔著一米多距離用電腦下單。菜單殘舊，感覺不太乾淨。建議可更換。
食物賣相OK，但湯麵和麻醬拌麵同樣偏鹹，另外點了青瓜和小香腸，小食算是可以接受。兩人點了四樣食物及一樣飲品，消費了170元，以油麻地區而言可接受。飲品份量不大。

用餐環境不算理想，若只想醫肚不失為就腳的地方。
吃了鹽酥雞拌麵加熱奶茶。鹽酥雞新鮮炸，熱辣辣又不鹹，麵很爽滑又QQ 地。奶茶多奶又滑口，茶又不似港式般扯肚皮，適合脾胃不好人士。總括來說很好吃又不太昂貴的平日午餐

食物及服務已沒有以前好，而且越來越差！

另外衛生也越來越差，蚊蟲蒼蠅放養的亂飛，飲品杯永遠都不會清乾淨，可以連著食物殘餘，而且立癡癡到菌黑，很髒！越來越失望。

重點再提，服務態度越來越差。

小吃由原來的鹽酥雞，入面很多都是麵粉，沒有了肉，變了鹽酥湯丸。
食物可以接受，有細碗飯選擇，比細食人士可以揀選。值得一試。😋😋
台式餐廳，較不錯的台式食品味道，不貴

result.adr_address: 530-538 Nathan Rd, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 530-538 Nathan Rd, Yau Ma Tei, Hong Kong
result.name: In's Point

reviews.text:
This place is crowded by many people. There's many small shops but full of small toys 😍 just try to look it carefully. I got my gang of princesses from here in the price that cheaper than Taiwan. I feel like here suitable for boys more than girls. If u love cute characters dolls maybe u should go to Sino Centre it's not far from this building. 
Ah..here only have 2 floors for shopping.

Very fantastic toy shopping experience, more than half of the toys (i tried to make a guess here) are at a very low price. And there is a range of many things! Although there might be quite crowded at most of the time, it will not diminish your treasure hunting mood.

One of the few places I buy most of my LEGO stuff from. Definitely as must-go if you're a LEGO fanatic, some shop owners are able to order certain sets for you as well. Do mind, it's better if you can communicate in Chinese, haha. But nonetheless, I'm sure they can help you.

Best place to buy toys @ relatively cheap prices. I was able to score some really good deals on Star Wars Black Series action figures. I'll definitely go back to check out the LEGO stores as well. I highly recommend putting this on your HK bucketlist.
Great place to search and find collectible toys when your in HK Kowloon side!  Highly recommended.

result.adr_address: 香港油麻地彌敦道530-538號
result.name: 現時點

reviews.text:
九龍區玩具店舖集中地，商場二/三樓內全為私人開辨的玩具小店，類型繁多，包括日，美figure，超合金，中古玩具，lego，扭旦，tomica等等，亦有二手玩具商店及格仔舖。但售賣模型類的商店較少。一些比較難找的玩具都有機會在這裡找到。喜歡玩具的一定來過這裡。
玩具價錢一般，不會太平，有時甚至有“炒“價，但勝在集中，要買心頭好的朋友最好多行一遍 ，以免買貴了。
商場環境較差，燈光不足，又由於商店面積太細，大多會將商品放出通道，令通道非常狹窄。再加上人流多，繁忙時間及假日會水洩不通。

要來這裡最方便是乘坐港鐵在油麻地店下車。

玩具愛好者很多都會"現時點" +"信和中心"+" 兆萬中心" 一起行。有興趣的朋友可找尋其他兩個商場看看。

現時點係一個比較多中古懷舊玩具為主既商場，裡面有兩層係賣玩具，有好幾間格仔鋪，每間格仔鋪都各有特式和主題，例如主要賣卡牌遊戲、毛公仔、可動手辦、玩具車等⋯⋯
在現時點五花八門的格仔鋪中尋寶真的可以花很多時間，而且現時點中的店鋪很多價錢都合理，
不只賣玩具，亦有電子遊戲，理髮店，餐廳，真的十分特別。
不過現時點的商舖面積都比較細，每間店幾乎只可以容納幾個人，而且人流比較多，不過也不會減少玩具迷對這地方的興趣！
因為像這樣的地方，香港真的越來越少！希望這特色可以一直持續下去！

This place is crowded by many people. There's many small shops but full of small toys 😍 just try to look it carefully. I got my gang of princesses from here in the price that cheaper than Taiwan. I feel like here suitable for boys more than girls. If u love cute characters dolls maybe u should go to Sino Centre it's not far from this building. 
Ah..here only have 2 floors for shopping.
潮物玩具集中地， 無論係大人去尋找兒時玩意、集體記憶; 還是小朋友去尋找潮流玩具， 務求要揸乾父母的荷包， 在這裏都可以心想事成。
